\par 
\par (3). If you get confused by the use of  pratyaharas like 'jash', 'khar' etc and want to know which phonemes they consist of, use }{\b\insrsid7553604\charrsid4922919 'Find Pratyahara' }{\insrsid7553604\charrsid4922919 
